H0.text: Dark matter is matter in the universe that does not emit light.

H1.text: Cold matter is the term for matter in the universe that does not emit light.

H2.text: Hidden matter is the matter in the universe that does not emit light.

H3.text: Black matter is matter in the universe that does not emit light.

A4.text: dark matter is an invisible and hypothetical form of matter that does not interact with light or other electromagnetic radiation
